        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"779183\">Janitha</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/287929-mathlib4/topic/Eventual.20Domination/near/529910020\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Indeed. I made a mistake. Sorry. I’m working in a special set of functions on natural numbers that contains the constant function 1, and the identity function, and which is closed under addition, multiplication, and exponentiation. Eventual domination is a well-ordering on it.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>then you have to prove that yourself</p>",
